DETECT PSIONICS: Sensing psionic activity nearby

Category: Psionic
Base skill: 30% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

This name covers two related but separate things. As a skill, it is
mundane trained sensitivity to psychic phenomena - noticing that
something psionic happened nearby, without any special power of your
own. As an actual psionic power, it is a real, castable ability with
its own cost and effect (see below); most characters who care about
detecting psionics will use the power, not the skill.

Command: psi detect psionics
  Costs 6 ISP. Detects psionic activity in the room for 2 minutes.
  Requires knowing the psionic power (a Psionic OCC ability), not
  just the mundane skill.

